Overview of Changes in libbean 1.29.0
=====================================

* libpeas 1.28.0 fork
* add FUNDING.yml
* update AUTHORS
* ci: enable Github Actions
* rename peas -> bean
* port from GTK to CTK
* bean-plugin-loader-python: avoid deprecated 'PyEval_InitThreads'
* Update translations
* update README
* tests: Explicitly depend on the GIR and typelib
